29:41.000Z","msg":"今次同兩老去，應該都冇機會"},{"pid":"c8bde983116e0dfa25eac2e8fc7721bf0bf91145","tid":899300,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"聽日去邊好 諗爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed6f096a070ad07b96ae8beff665941fbbcef3b","tid":899300,"uid":72188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:54:42.000Z","msg":"今朝早咬左個包就上機到呢家<br />\n肚餓到傻，快快手check in完，去左搵野食，所以呢家補番文<br />\n京都呢兩晚住呢間<br />\nCross hotel Kyoto <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/205307_92176922761530ef69170dacf3f01326.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F205307_92176922761530ef69170dacf3f01326.png&h=eae6a2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/214813_8b495c65def489b7c27b8fc40ee32e67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F214813_8b495c65def489b7c27b8fc40ee32e67.png&h=45d40bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說好似係新酒店，位置係三条車站附近都算方便<br />\n房都算闊落，同埋都打埋得乾淨（我通常習慣會睇窗邊多唔多塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ）<br />\n<br />\n然後就狗衝去左先斗町搵野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/220827_6a3db9d465c07832905dad97d5bf4036.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F220827_6a3db9d465c07832905dad97d5bf4036.png&h=915c8c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本諗住食柚子元打邊爐，但佢岩岩last order 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著我老豆話求其入一間食都得，結果我就好是旦咁入，結果入左一間門口乜menu 都冇，完唔知有咩食既既舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/220949_53069f9de466c15d1f27b41ee9193eba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F220949_53069f9de466c15d1f27b41ee9193eba.png&h=517a9fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/220950_a45499d0b43ad0a936731a58304c3694.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F220950_a45499d0b43ad0a936731a58304c3694.png&h=273542b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/220956_78acb95a0ddf54a1639fc9081853b711.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F220956_78acb95a0ddf54a1639fc9081853b711.png&h=4c6b5ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/220959_9ca4b4077b6083b947aa693d5e6920ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F220959_9ca4b4077b6083b947aa693d5e6920ed.png&h=6b101529&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/221002_0490fc043b8d7c38f1f2a76db4dbbc67.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F221002_0490fc043b8d7c38f1f2a76db4dbbc67.png&h=cf1a9a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本原來係大阪燒，我地呢個係牛肉味，另外仲叫左支啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實原本應該我地自己整，但老板娘好好人，怕我地唔識幫我地整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n味道真心唔覺得好特別，但可能我地真係好肚餓，所以比我地秒殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （由於份量唔大，所以encore 左份豬肉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n由於我地都仲係覺得肚餓，所以再搵野食<br />\n行番出木屋町通，見到呢間拉麵，又係諗都冇諗就入左去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/223912_489da02a700f2a168ecff782183f53c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F223912_489da02a700f2a168ecff782183f53c6.png&h=77c2e2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/223914_90be0071f3b491f8b8639247dc0ef881.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F223914_90be0071f3b491f8b8639247dc0ef881.png&h=4e737659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我叫左呢個，牛輾麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/224253_77db94d92db95c5ed22ced1e70dca2e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F224253_77db94d92db95c5ed22ced1e70dca2e6.png&h=b3dc4787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個湯濃得黎唔鹹，麵係幼麵，我幾鐘意，唔算話係好好好食，但醫肚黎講真係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/225032_4a4658444f4904c8f92d78430a2082de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F225032_4a4658444f4904c8f92d78430a2082de.png&h=76d3bba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下舊肥膏幾邪惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢話係牛展，但我食落覺得似坑腩"},{"pid":"a12599aef50d51f0c95080d736a8c94e23a69bd6","tid":899300,"uid":72188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8bde983116e0dfa25eac2e8fc7721bf0bf91145","tid":899300,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"聽日去邊好 諗爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"聽日我會上比叡山，時間充足會去埋貴船（唔夠時間就睇夜楓），但都想留番d時間行下河原町新京極果邊"},{"pid":"ebff5721fb7c2ce4c953c62f8d211af7a427c52f","tid":899300,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12599aef50d51f0c95080d736a8c94e23a69bd6","tid":899300,"uid":72188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8bde983116e0dfa25eac2e8fc7721bf0bf91145","tid":899300,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"聽日去邊好 諗爆頭<img src=\"/assets